{"tid":942951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖流出) 台灣36F辣媽與12歲兒「全裸共浴」的　掀倫理爭議","createTime":"2018-12-16T07:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T06:50:52.000Z","uid":16697,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"caa2f78cecc609852824bb65c3c0f8de4b5239e0","tid":942951,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/photo/bkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181216134540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181216134540&h=5d157b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/photo/bkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_02p.jpg?20181216134540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20181216134540&h=050bd27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/photo/bkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_03p.jpg?20181216134540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_03p.jpg%3F20181216134540&h=842eb759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">台灣擁有36F驕人上圍的朱姓單親辣媽「紫米」，近日於網上分享一張與其12歲兒子「全裸共浴」的照片，拍照期間二人又做出「V字」手勢，可見母子感情融洽。紫米更指，每周會和兒子「共浴」一次，事件引起網民熱議。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n紫米發相原意其實是想與網民聊聊育兒經，了解其他家長有否與孩子共浴的習慣，「你們都跟孩子們一起洗澡嗎？洗到幾歲呢？」紫米表示，雖然兒子已經12歲，但母子倆一周至少共浴一次。她認為自覺需要多點陪兒子，亦很珍惜和他一起洗澡的日子，「當他會主動拒絕你時，就是進入青春期了」。<br />\n<br />\n她亦稱，日本人也會一家人共浴，希望網民不要戴有色眼鏡去看，更稱當兒子習慣看媽媽的胴體，就不會對女性身體產生好奇，對其心理會較更健康。不過她亦坦承，若然換成父女，就似乎不太適合。<br />\n<br />\n對於辣媽母子共浴一事，有大批網民批評，指孩子快到青春期，如此年紀下還和母親赤裸共浴有違倫理，並質疑「這樣不會出問題嗎？」、「現在孩子發育得早，這樣感覺怪怪的！」<br />\n<br />\n不過有網民就支持稱，母子共浴可增進親子關係，同時可灌輸正確的性觀念，事件至今仍引起廣泛迴響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/bkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181216%2Fbkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001.html&d=2DedmL28IKyHTBDmuYRUIP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5d54bda7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/bkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcf9a22112186fbc5aeffc70e2ddda6d29113d1","tid":942951,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"依條新聞究竟要po幾多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0968dd4ec94350e98a338b8d358b158442c0f141","tid":942951,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:42:43.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30732fcf138ac67650a8d60eb7460d1ecf536446","tid":942951,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"edcf9a22112186fbc5aeffc70e2ddda6d29113d1","tid":942951,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"依條新聞究竟要po幾多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"撚好似你咁撚得閒望住有冇出過同樣新聞咩毒撚"},{"pid":"1b62d178e51e747bc4c041ac4acb778a0c0e5f2b","tid":942951,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"30732fcf138ac67650a8d60eb7460d1ecf536446","tid":942951,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"edcf9a22112186fbc5aeffc70e2ddda6d29113d1","tid":942951,"uid":38904,"like